  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Delve into the World of Absence of Light: Embark on an Epic Action RPG Adventure in Cloudia! 🗡️ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/2e9387b01533351fdcc603ec32907a5f.poster.avif?t=1766851823\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/2e9387b01533351fdcc603ec32907a5f.webm?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/2e9387b01533351fdcc603ec32907a5f.mp4?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 Immerse yourself in the captivating realm of Absence of Light, set in the mesmerizing world of Cloudia! Prepare to be mesmerized by a medieval-inspired journey, where mystical treasures and powerful weapons await your discovery. Take control of a heroic character and forge your arsenal with diverse weapons, each possessing unique attributes to strategically unleash devastating attacks upon the forces of darkness that now rule the once-glorious Old Realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/ced419901dc635da5b85823810f258a7.poster.avif?t=1766851823\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/ced419901dc635da5b85823810f258a7.webm?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/ced419901dc635da5b85823810f258a7.mp4?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 Unleash the Power of Action RPG Gameplay: face challenging battles, and uncover hidden secrets in an immersive gaming experience that will keep you hooked for hours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/2fe744752e8624d4ca19f147d6b72146.poster.avif?t=1766851823\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/2fe744752e8624d4ca19f147d6b72146.webm?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/2fe744752e8624d4ca19f147d6b72146.mp4?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏰 Discover the Enchanting Realm of Cloudia: Traverse through the charming village area, interact with intriguing characters, and collect valuable items that will aid you in your quest to restore light to Cloudia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/76a27a0e76633132e2959595294e799e.poster.avif?t=1766851823\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/76a27a0e76633132e2959595294e799e.webm?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/76a27a0e76633132e2959595294e799e.mp4?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ Master Formidable Combos: Choose your weapons wisely and create powerful combinations to conquer the darkness and bring back the radiance to Cloudia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/f5a682e4e1823d6dfac5d56c72bf3df2.poster.avif?t=1766851823\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/f5a682e4e1823d6dfac5d56c72bf3df2.webm?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536710/extras/f5a682e4e1823d6dfac5d56c72bf3df2.mp4?t=1766851823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📜 Unravel the Prologue: The fate of Cloudia hangs in the balance, and only your courage can shatter the sinister grasp of the shadows. Are you ready to become a legend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 Join the Gaming Community: Connect with fellow adventurers, share tips, and showcase your achievements in Cloudia. Get ready for epic battles and unforgettable moments!</p>",
